trans-unit.source: When the `DocumentCompleted` event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: När den `DocumentCompleted` händelse inträffar nytt dokument laddas fullständigt, vilket innebär att du kan komma åt innehållet via den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>

trans-unit.source: Handling this event lets you cancel navigation if certain conditions have not been met, for example, when the user has not completely filled out a form.
